---
import Apple from '../../public/assets/stores/icon-appstore.svg'
---
<!-- Hero -->
<section class="max-w-[85rem] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 relative overflow-hidden before:absolute before:top-0 before:start-1/2 before:bg-[url('https://preline.co/assets/svg/examples/squared-bg-element.svg')] before:bg-no-repeat before:bg-top before:size-full before:-z-[1] before:transform before:-translate-x-1/2">
	<!-- Grid -->
	<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8 xl:gap-20 md:items-center">
	  	<div>
			<h1 class="block text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl lg:leading-tigh">Obtén tu licencia de conducir a la primera con <span class="text-primary-100">TestDrive</span></h1>
			<p class="mt-3 text-lg text-gray-500">Todo el contenido que necesitas para aprobar de forma éxitosa el examen de conducir clase B en un solo lugar. Acceso Gratis y Contenido Premium!</p>
  
			<!-- Buttons -->
			<div class="mt-7 grid gap-3 w-full sm:inline-flex">
		  		<a href="https://apps.apple.com/cl/app/testdrive-chile/id6477247367">
					<img src="./assets/stores/icon-appstore.svg">
				</a>
				<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.testdrive.chile">
					<img src="./assets/stores/icon-google-play.svg">
				</a>
				</div>
	  			</div>
	  			<!-- End Col -->
  
	 		<div class="relative ms-4 flex justify-center items-center">
			<img class="w-96" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1648737963503-1a26da876aca?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&h=900&q=80" alt="Image Description">
     	</div>
	  <!-- End Col -->
	</div>
</section>
  <!-- End Hero -->